5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Strategy First. <br/> <span class=\"text-electric-blue\">Results Always.</span></h2><p class=\"text-grey text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Our philosophy is simple: we prioritize business outcomes over vanity metrics. Every line of code and every pixel is designed to drive growth.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mt-12\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-2 tracking-tight\">Nigerian Market Mastery</h4><p class=\"text-grey text-xs leading-relaxed\">12+ years of local expertise combined with international standards to build brands that resonate.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-2 tracking-tight\">End-to-End Solutions</h4><p class=\"text-grey text-xs leading-relaxed\">From strategy and design to development and marketing — we handle the full growth cycle.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-2 tracking-tight\">Performance First</h4><p class=\"text-grey text-xs leading-relaxed\">We don&#x27;t just build beautiful things; we build assets that deliver measurable ROI and scale.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-2 tracking-tight\">Strategic Partnership</h4><p class=\"text-grey text-xs leading-relaxed\">We act as your extended tech team, providing continuous support and strategic consulting.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"glass p-12 relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><div class=\"text-electric-blue mb-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight\">&quot;They didn&#x27;t just build our website — they built our entire digital presence from the ground up. The ROI was visible within the first quarter.&quot;              </blockquote><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-midnight-lt border border-electric-blue/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-electric-blue\">TA</div><div><div class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm\">Tunde Adeyemi</div><div class=\"text-grey text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest\">CEO — Adeyemi Logistics</div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 border border-electric-blue/20 -z-0\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-60 h-60 bg-electric-blue/5 blur-3xl -z-0\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\"><div class=\"bg-electric-blue p-16 md:p-24 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-20 bg-[url(&#x27;https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg&#x27;)] pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-tight\">Ready to Scale Your <br/> Digital Authority?</h2><p class=\"text-white/80 text-lg mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto\">Book a free strategy session today. Let&#x27;s map out your growth trajectory with precision.</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-midnight text-white px-12 py-5 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-midnight-lt transition-all hover:scale-105\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started Now</a></div></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hephzibah Media Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async